values:
I am sooo bored right now..there is nothin to do.  Today was kinda boring i went to church and then went to a baby shower.  After that i came home and took a nap cuz i was really tired.  I can get back on im tomorrow thank god.  i only have 6 days until i leave...i cant wait i am finally gettin out of auburn and goin someplace hot!  I just found out where we are goin...i guess my mom and i are goin to Fort Myers and then to West Palm, should be fun.  Right now i am watchin Miss Congeniality, but i might go out for a bikeride cuz i forgot my sneakers so i cant go running.  Nothin else is new..oh except that drama this year is goin to stink and we're deff not ready.  I'm very disappointed in the Yankees right now..they lost today to the Orioles 7-2 ..thats really not cool at all!  They better win tomorrow thats all i have to say.  Well idk what else to say so i guess ill go and play XBox or somethin.  talk to everyone lata..bye!
                                                ~Ash

Wow i havent written in here in a long time.  i just got back from hanging with tim all day...it was fun!  great times with mason and chaz and jim and cody(cueball)  haha just messin cody.  i cannot wait until mon..i can finally get back on im, i never knew how much i would miss gettin on that until i was grounded from it.  and i only have 3 days left of wearing chapel clothes :-)  ppl they just get me mad thats all.  nothin else new really except that my mom and i are prolly moving soon..and i cant wait cuz i need to get away from the drunks upstairs.  this time next week i will be in FL with my mom and my adopted grandparents...i cant wait we are goin to have a blast.  my mom and i are goin on an air boat through the everglades and then we're going kiakin...ive never done that before but that should be fun.  i just am really looking forward to getting out of auburn and hangin on the beach, getting a tan.  well listen i am bored and theres nothin to do here im home by myself, so i guess i will write sometime later..bye everyone.
                                                   ~Ash
PS duck tape is the solution to every problem...right guys????  haha ;-)

hey guys whats happening?  well its finally Friday..thank goodness ive been waiting all week for it to come.  This weekend is going to be a lot of studying for tests and quizzes, what else is new?  lol well i had a pretty good day today.  im about to go to someone's house for pizza and just to hang out so ill talk to you all later!  bye
